<refentry xml:id="vtiful-kernel-excel.getDataValidations" xmlns="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink">
 <refnamediv>
  <refname>Vtiful\Kernel\Excel::getDataValidations</refname>
  <refpurpose>Vtiful\Kernel\Excel getDataValidations</refpurpose>
 </refnamediv>
 <refsect1 role="description">
  &reftitle.description;
  <methodsynopsis>
   <modifier>public</modifier> <type>array</type><methodname>Vtiful\Kernel\Excel::getDataValidations</methodname>
   <void/>
  </methodsynopsis>
  <simpara>Returns the data validation rules defined on the worksheet currently open for reading.</simpara>
 </refsect1>
 <refsect1 role="parameters">
  &reftitle.parameters;
  &no.function.parameters;
 </refsect1>
 <refsect1 role="returnvalues">
  &reftitle.returnvalues;
  <simpara>An array of data validation rules, each entry an associative array with the keys <literal>type</literal>, <literal>operator</literal>, <literal>formula1</literal>, <literal>formula2</literal>, <literal>allow_blank</literal>, <literal>show_drop_down</literal>, <literal>show_input_message</literal>, <literal>show_error_message</literal>, <literal>error_style</literal>, <literal>prompt</literal>, <literal>prompt_title</literal>, <literal>error</literal>, <literal>error_title</literal> and <literal>sqref</literal> (the cell range the rule applies to). Returns &null; when no worksheet is open for reading.</simpara>
 </refsect1>
</refentry>
